Mayer Award from the American

00:00:34.210 --> 00:00:37.440
Physical Society, the Radcliffe
Institute for Advanced Study

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:40.570
Fellowships, the Bart
Bok Prize from Harvard,

00:00:40.570 --> 00:00:43.231
and the Miller Institute
Professorship from Berkeley.

00:00:43.231 --> 00:00:44.980
She serves on a large
number of committees

00:00:44.980 --> 00:00:47.470
for NASA and the National
Science Foundation.

00:00:47.470 --> 00:00:50.350
She's a chair of the Science
and Technology Definition Team

00:00:50.350 --> 00:00:54.600
for NASA's next large x-ray
mission concept in Lynx.

00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:56.990
And she frequently appears
in TV documentaries

00:00:56.990 --> 00:01:00.640
